text: Got a quick bite at Subway before running errands. I was not expecting much. However, it turned out to be the best subway I have ever had. The honey oat bread was toasted to perfection and the staff was generous with the fillings. Enjoyed every bite. Would definitely come back to this Subway again.

Brought my family here for dinner. We were served by Augusto and Maha. They were very patient and helpful in assisting us in the ordering process. Most importantly, we felt very welcome by their smiles
Not too many people. The guys working here are very enthusiastic with their work so I'm giving them a very good rating.

Absolutely love the service of Augusto. I always feel welcomed whenever I drop by this outlet and he is super friendly. There is always a warm welcome whenever he is working & a smiling face. He is very fast and able to multitask very well too. Thank you for your good service! :)

We enjoyed the food and the service crews are very accomodating

Travelling from Philippines
